<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī sundara</hi> pāṇṭiya tevaṟku yāṇṭu
<lb n="2"/><num value="10"><g type="numeral">10</g></num> Āvatiṉetiriraṇṭāvatu vikkaramaciṅ
<lb n="3"/>ka tevaṉ Ōlai mutaliyār tirumaṭattukku <unclear>ti</unclear>
<lb n="4"/>ru viḷakkeṇṇaikkum tayiramutu <unclear>p</unclear>ā
<lb n="5"/>lamutukkum ko <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="6"/>ntavarippaṭi Uḷḷa kaṭamai kuṭimaika
<lb n="7"/>ḷum kuṭikkalamuṭpaṭṭa maṟṟum <unclear>Ep</unclear>
<lb n="8"/>peṟpaṭṭaṉavum <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="9"/><hi rend="grantha">śaṣa</hi>mākak kuṭuttom Ippaṭi kallilum
<lb n="10"/>cempilum <hi rend="grantha">candrādi</hi>tavaṟ celvatākak ka
<lb n="11"/>llilum cempilu veṭṭik koḷka Ivai
<lb n="12"/>vikkaramaciṅkateva neḻuttu Ippa
<lb n="13"/>ṭikkut tennava taraiyaṉ Eḻuttu
<lb n="14"/>Ippaṭikku <unclear>kāṉa</unclear> nāṭāḻvān Eḻuttu
<lb n="15"/><hi rend="grantha">śrī māhe <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> </hi>
